title: Fiat Bravo/a Workshop Service Manuals
description:
Fiat Bravo -Brava Workshop Manuals
----------------------------------
 
Service and Workshop Manuals - Volumes 1 to 4 in PDF Format (English Only)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------


Engines / Models Covered 1996 - 2001:

Petrol Models:

1.2 - 1242 16V (MK2)

1.4 - 1370 12V (MK1)

1.6 - 1581 16V (MK1 & MK2)

1.8 - 1747 16V (MK1 & MK2)

2.0 - 1998 20V (MK1 & MK2)

Diesel Models:

1.9 - 1929 DIESEL (MK1)

1.9 - 1910 TD 75 (MK1)

1.9 - 1910 TD 100 (MK1)

1.9 - 1910 JTD105 (MK2)
 

This file contains all aspects of service and repair of your Bravo - Brava

 
These are the manuals Fiat give to their mechanics to help them service your Fiat Bravo - Brava

 

Here are just some of the things covered by these manuals...

 
ENGINES

ELECTRICS

TRANSMISSION

CLUTCH

BODYWORK & PANELS

GEARBOX

EXHAUST SYSTEMS

CATALYCTIC CONVERTERS
WHEELS

TOWING & JACKING PROCEDURES

BRAKES

SUSPENSION

COOLING SYSTEMS
INTERIOR & EXTERIOR FIXTURES & FITTINGS

IN CAR AUDIO/VIDEO
NAVIGATION SYSTEM

TYRES
